ntopng categorizes hosts using services are provided by http://block.si

In order to use these categorization services you need to mail info@block.si and
ask for a test key to be used in ntopng or go to http://www.blocksi.net/blocksi-api.php

Once you have the key available, you can start
ntopng -c KEY ...


NOTES:
- THIS IS AN EXPERIMENTAL SERVICE
- NTOPNG WILL CONTACT DIRECTLY BLOCK.SI (NO TRAFFIC WILL PASS THROUGH NTOP.ORG)
- NTOP HAS NO BUSINESS RELATIONSHIP WITH BLOCK.SI